        {
            "title": "A股半日跌深股跌0.65%   晶片股揚   家電股回落",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日報跌，深股跑輸，芯片股逆市升，家電股回落。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日跌12點或0.39%，報3198點，今早開報3211點，平開，最高見3220，升9點或0.28%，隨即反覆向下，最低見3192點，跌19點或0.59%，半日成交2962.63億元(人民幣‧下同)</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報9910點，跌65點或0.65%，今早開報9957點，跌19點或0.19%，最高見10004，升28點或0.28%，其後轉跌，約10:00AM低9697點，跌79點或0.79%，半日成交4343.17億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日跌17點或0.46%，報3762點，今早開報3778點，跌1點或0.03%。<br/>   創板指數半日跌10點或0.5%，報2000點，今早開報2006點，跌4點或0.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬科(000002.SZ)跌2.88%，報6.75元 ; 紅星美凱龍(601828.SH)跌2.58%，報3.02元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海爾智家(600690.SH)跌2.99%，報28.59元 ; 美的(000333.SZ)跌2.18%，報77.01</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">福萊特玻璃(601865.SH)跌3.96%，18.44元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(688981.SH)升3.64%，報94.64元 ; 華虹(688347.SH)升2.61%，報43.32元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14626561-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c0-65-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a-%e5%ae%b6%e9%9b%bb%e8%82%a1%e5%9b%9e%e8%90%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240205_FI_source-ap_A-SHARE.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 11:55:24",
